{"id":440191,"date":[{"year":1963,"month":2,"day":7}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"262","ytitle":"","mtitle":"春夜","ftitle":"","authors":["肖岗"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"肖岗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月到三更上窗台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一树腊梅含新瓣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屋里合家人意好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷把酒祝新岁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新裁布袄红花配，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满脸皱纹都笑开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起酒杯感谢党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社万年春长在。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拍拍胸膛象打雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清清嗓门又一杯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指着墙上新奖状，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号召合家大竞赛:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人知勤俭地不懒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腊月河泥干金贵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全家编个劳动组，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老小首战年初三!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷举起第三杯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚滚春潮杯中来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿子要跟爹挑战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"媳妇要上罱泥船。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十岁闺女管春花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五岁孙孙扫鸡塮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老伴急得拍了腿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要和媳妇轮班干!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酒过三杯兴更浓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一对春联拈口来:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去岁一人当先进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今春全家争模范!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那知月牙过了墙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几枝腊梅进窗台。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁处村上鞭炮响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恰似春雷动地来!"}]}